This paper is about multi-agent reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) is the most likely category. The paper also deals with communication between agents, which falls under the subfield of natural language processing, making cs.CL (Computation and Language) a likely category as well. The paper also involves coordination between multiple agents, which falls under the subfield of robotics, making cs.RO (Robotics) a possible category. Additionally, the paper deals with cooperative tasks, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence, making cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) a likely category. Finally, the paper deals with multi-agent systems, making cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) a possible category.
